---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Work On Yourself — Soul Care for Leaders"
	description="A twelve-month Soul Care Intensive for leaders whose outer success has outpaced their inner life."
>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-white px-6 py-20 lg:py-28 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
					<div class="hero-stagger">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-4">Work On Yourself</p>
						<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-gray-900">A Soul Care Intensive<br /><span class="text-red-600">for Leaders</span></h1>
						<p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-xl">Whose outer success has outpaced their inner life.</p>
						<div class="mt-8">
							<a href="https://workonyourself.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-md bg-red-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-red-700">Visit WorkOnYourself.com →</a>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="hidden lg:grid grid-cols-3 gap-3" aria-hidden="true" data-animate="zoom-in">
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-600 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-800 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-600 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-900 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-700 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-800 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-600 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-gray-900 aspect-square"></div>
						<div class="rounded-2xl bg-red-800 aspect-square"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE CHALLENGE -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">The Challenge</p>
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">When Success Outpaces the Soul</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">You built the business. You carry the influence. You've been rewarded for your capacity to think, decide, and deliver. But somewhere along the way, the soul went untended.</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="3">Stress became normal. Margin disappeared. Faith endured without intimacy. You are physically present but emotionally numb. Highly successful — yet lacking any genuine sense of significance.</p>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="4">When leaders like you seek help, they encounter a fragmented landscape: therapy disconnected from faith, coaching focused on performance, retreats without long-term integration. No one integrates the full journey within a single pastorally stewarded container.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE SOLUTION -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-3" data-animate="fade-up">The Solution</p>
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Until Now.</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">Work On Yourself is a twelve-month Soul Care Intensive — pastorally stewarded, relationally grounded, and theologically centered on restoration to God as Father. This is not therapy, coaching, or a retreat. It is a protected season where leaders are accompanied rather than optimized, stewarded rather than evaluated.</p>
				<blockquote class="bg-navy-950 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 my-8" data-animate="fade-in" data-delay="3">
					<p class="font-serif text-xl italic leading-relaxed">"And what do you benefit if you gain the whole world but lose your own soul?"</p>
					<cite class="block mt-3 text-sm font-semibold text-red-400 not-italic">— Mark 8:36 (FHB)</cite>
				</blockquote>
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="4">Stewarded by Kevin and Shelly White.</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- CTA -->
		<section class="bg-red-600 px-6 py-20 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-white sm:text-4xl mb-4" data-animate="fade-up">Ready to Begin the Journey?</h2>
				<p class="text-red-100 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="1">Work On Yourself is for leaders ready to prioritize their inner life with the same intentionality they bring to their outer one.</p>
				<a href="https://workonyourself.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-md hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="2">WorkOnYourself.com →</a>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
